Definition: the code of law derived from the Koran and from the teachings and example of Mohammed
Example: sharia is only applicable to Muslims; under Islamic law there is no separation of church and state
Synonyms: shariah_law, sharia, sharia_law, Islamic_law, law, the, code, of, derived, from, Koran, and, teachings, example, Mohammed, is, only, applicable, to, Muslims, under, Islamic, there, no, separation, church, state
Category: noun.group
